        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Although Israel had effected a settlement in Canaan, the history seems to show that down to the times of David the tribal boundaries were subject to great fluctuation, and the inroads of surrounding peoples made their tenure very uncertain.",
        "children": []
